  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study aims to provide preliminary data on the feasibility and outcomes of a 12 week
      exercise program on the quality of life of men with hormone refractory prostate cancer
      receiving docetaxel-based chemotherapy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
